1778516754191121	reckon-dev	itc:v3:AWLk8kz5M8ySZQAAAAAAQevVvre1WgAAAAEvHA		item.create	bn-3k3	{"description":"Per-file state: previous_totals = zeros; active_model = None.\n- payload.type == \"session_meta\": reset previous_totals; record session_id.\n- payload.type == \"turn_context\": switch active_model.\n- payload.type == \"token_count\": emit UsageEvent with deltas = max(0, current - previous); update previous.\nTokens: input_tokens, cached_input_tokens→cache_read, output_tokens, reasoning_output_tokens→reasoning.\nSessions whose first token_count event is absent (pre-2025-09-06) → skip silently.\nproptest: negative deltas clamp; model changes reset the carry; gaps don't double-count.\n","kind":"task","parent":"bn-1gn","size":"m","title":"Codex reader: cumulative→delta state machine"}	blake3:3SPc2Ejp1JCouOCDpU10WboOjF9Mzc4ztnFptILtQMk
1778516754300223	reckon-dev	itc:v3:AWLk8kz5M8ySZQAAAAAAQevVvre1WgAAAAEvHQ		item.create	bn-26r	{"description":"Codex slugs (gpt-5.2-2025-..., gpt-4.1-2025-..., o1-2024-...) → openai/gpt-5.2 etc.\nPi provider+modelId composition: \"{provider}/{modelId}\" (e.g. anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5 → anthropic/claude-haiku-4.5).\n","kind":"task","parent":"bn-1gn","size":"xs","title":"model_map: openai/* + pi vendor passthrough"}	blake3:aEYW5gC4119oXbWJOlR-WJvymYtXSNyvbeCtLHSmDFI
