1778516754866842	reckon-dev	itc:v3:AWLk8kz5M8ySZQAAAAAAQevVvre1WgAAAAEvIg		item.create	bn-yl3	{"description":"Build the HttpClientBuilder with tls + tls-webpki-roots, user-agent \"reckon/<version>\".\nAuth lookup order: RECKON_OPENROUTER_KEY env → OPENROUTER_API_KEY env → ~/.config/reckon/config.toml `openrouter.key`.\nNever log the key; mask to last 4 chars in any diagnostic.\n","kind":"task","parent":"bn-6a7","size":"s","title":"OpenRouter HTTP client + auth lookup chain"}	blake3:3M3V6rJls178Ia6U9C3QjD4Zkiq1Go5UOjzmbL7Gqx0
