1778529075801959	reckon-dev/0/calm-junction	itc:v3:AWKZkkmSZJJMmTnEAAAAQbaq1aqta7gAAAE2AQ		item.comment	bn-vcy	{"body":"Completed: LiteLLM pricing fetcher with 7-day TTL cache\n\nImplemented:\n- is_pricing_cache_stale() to check if cache needs refresh (>7 days or missing)\n- load_pricing_from_cache() to load cache + merge with vendored fallback\n- pricing_refresh module with fetch_and_cache_pricing() that:\n  - Fetches from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BerriAI/litellm/main/model_prices_and_context_window.json\n  - Writes via atomic temp -> rename\n  - Handles failures gracefully with error return\n- Non-blocking background thread spawning in main.rs\n- Single stderr warning on fetch failure\n- Comprehensive tests for staleness detection, cache merging, and fallback union\n\nAll acceptance criteria met:\n✓ Stale cache detection (>7d)\n✓ Fresh cache detection (no HTTP call)\n✓ Atomic writes with temp file\n✓ Non-blocking fetch task\n✓ Cached + fallback merger with precedence\n\nAll tests passing (59 total)."}	blake3:NeH7fjpU23URANAoSWVYnpy5BsjdT3NBGCXp38Ew0MY
