1778531162666309	reckon-dev/0/scarlet-crow	itc:v3:AWLJMyZOZJnJ5lAAAAAAQdW1rtW69oAAAAExAQ		item.comment	bn-32h	{"body":"Completed: Extended model_map::canonical for Gemini and OpenCode.\n\nGemini implementation:\n- gemini-2.5-pro -> google/gemini-2.5-pro\n- gemini-2.5-flash-* -> google/gemini-2.5-flash\n- gemini-1.5-* -> google/gemini-1.5-*\n\nOpenCode implementation:\n- Passes through vendor/model format (e.g., openai/gpt-5.2)\n- Composes with provider_id if bare model_id (e.g., gpt-5.2 + openai provider -> openai/gpt-5.2)\n\nTests added:\n✅ 3 Gemini variants (2.5-pro, 2.5-flash with suffix, 1.5-pro with suffix)\n✅ 3 OpenCode forms (slashed, bare with provider, bare without provider)\n✅ All 22 model_map tests pass\n✅ All 53 library tests pass\n✅ Code compiles without errors\n\nPricing integration verified:\n- Pricing file contains openrouter/google/gemini-* entries that resolve to google/gemini-*\n- Pricing file contains openrouter/anthropic/claude-* and openrouter/openai/gpt-* entries that resolve correctly\n- Model lookup in pricing HashMap will succeed for all Gemini and OpenCode models\n\nNote: Full acceptance criterion (running with Gemini+OpenCode sources showing no Unknown pricing warnings) will be verified once Gemini reader (bn-8ou) and OpenCode reader are integrated into main.rs. The readers are already calling model_map::canonical correctly."}	blake3:WsXId4y6PbRqOVR33YxGK8pSF4s1oO_OcGwYOphMvTE
